Long-term sutimlimab improves quality of life for patients with cold agglutinin 
disease: CARDINAL 2-year follow-up.

Röth A(1), Broome CM(2), Barcellini W(3), Tvedt THA(4), Miyakawa Y(5), D'Sa 
S(6), Cella D(7), Bozzi S(8), Jayawardene D(9), Yoo R(9), Shafer F(9), Wardęcki 
